snippet: The Wimbledon champion Andy Murray rallied for a 4-6, 6-3, 6-2 victory over the unseeded Czech Lukas Rosol to reach the third round of the PNB Paribas Open in Indian Wells, Calif.
abstract: Roger Federer, Andy Murray and Stanislas Wawrinka advance to third round of the BNP Paribas Open.
lead_paragraph: The Wimbledon champion Andy Murray rallied for a 4-6, 6-3, 6-2 victory over the unseeded Czech Lukas Rosol to reach the third round of the PNB Paribas Open in Indian Wells, Calif.
